Minimal testharness.js subset for FastRender
===========================================

This directory contains a small, API-compatible subset of the WPT `testharness.js`
and `testharnessreport.js` scripts, implemented specifically for FastRender’s
offline `tests/wpt_dom/` smoke corpus.

It is intentionally not a verbatim copy of upstream WPT at this stage (the full
upstream harness is significantly larger). Once the JS runtime and WPT runner are
implemented, we should prefer vendoring upstream WPT copies and pinning the exact
upstream commit.

